data.description: Located in an undisturbed and well-managed neighborhood, this clean and ready to move into, end-unit townhome sits on a fantastic lot overlooking protected wetland and trees in the backyard. The easy, one-level living floor plan features a wide-open concept with vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace in the family/dining rooms, spacious, eat-in kitchen with access to the two-car attached garage with epoxy floor, private Owner’s suite with walk-in closet and ¾ en suite, and second bedroom with adjacent full bath. Also appreciate a designated laundry room with new washer/dryer and French door entry to a cozy sunroom with serene views of nature and access to the patio in back. Other improvements include newer furnace, AC and water softener, new flooring in kitchen and sunroom, roof, windows, and more. Excellent location- just steps from Ojibway Park, plus close to trails, shopping, restaurants and schools, with easy access to I-494.
